{"tid":854100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一帶一路關鍵國家　巴基斯坦「缺水」向IMF求救","createTime":"2018-10-09T06:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T08:24:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"154d2879ac1515ddba50ba49bf091fbcea0d8e1f","tid":854100,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:35:18.000Z","msg":"中國「一帶一路」倡議關鍵國家巴基斯坦，因財困將向國際貨幣基金組織（IMF）求援。惟《路透》報道，IMF稱目前巴基斯坦仍未正式提出要求援助。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>財政部長稱最少缺80億美元</strong><br />\n<br />\n該國財政部長Asad Umar昨晚（10月8日）發表聲明，表示該國財政儲備起碼有80億元（美元‧下同）缺口。自7月新總理Imran Khan上台之後，雖然該國與盟友包括沙特阿拉伯等國家的官員互訪，但對方都沒有提供支援。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>上周削減一帶一路鐵路貸款</strong><br />\n<br />\nImran Khan指出，目前該國的糟糕形勢，是上一任政府造成的。他指出：「巴基斯坦正遭受巨大的內部和外部債務壓力，而這一切是由前任政府的腐敗造成的。」<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦是中國「一帶一路」倡議的重點國家，原計劃在該國港口興建鐵路連接中國境內，上星期政府向表示要削減該鐵路貸款規模20億元，因巴基斯坦無法承擔該筆債務。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>外匯儲備僅僅夠還年底債務</strong><br />\n<br />\n該國外匯儲備在9月底已經減少至84億元，僅僅夠支付年底到期的主權債務。<br />\n<br />\nAsad Umar指出，與IMF商討的目的，是以「穩定復甦計劃」來處理國家的經濟危機，但沒有說明今次的融資額度。而他在8月向《彭博》透露，政府可能需要超過120億元。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>IMF已警告要迅速得到資金</strong><br />\n<br />\nIMF上星期已經警告巴基斯坦，要迅速得到外部融資，才能避免經濟危機。<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦財政一向不健全，是自1980年以來第13次向IMF求助，對上一次是5年之前。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而IMF最大捐款者美國曾提出質疑，擔心該國會用借來的資金去還中國的債務。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4/244711/%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6-%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6-%E7%BC%BA%E6%B0%B4-%E5%90%91imf%E6%B1%82%E6%95%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%2F244711%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2597%259C%25E9%258D%25B5%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%259D%25A6-%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E5%2590%2591imf%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%2595%2591&d=lb9mAeaxn1WEdioOs5bZikkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=0b09f7b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4/244711/%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6-%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6-%E7%BC%BA%E6%B0%B4-%E5%90%91imf%E6%B1%82%E6%95%91</a>"},{"pid":"3f365fd6bce34e02b1f6604623c493d50eaebfc9","tid":854100,"uid":4917,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T07:15:08.000Z","msg":"佢伊斯蘭咁有錢，去問佢兄弟拎啦"},{"pid":"b6cb320bde99906f9fdbe2f5d2f55301835918e9","tid":854100,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f365fd6bce34e02b1f6604623c493d50eaebfc9","tid":854100,"uid":4917,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T07:15:08.000Z","msg":"佢伊斯蘭咁有錢，去問佢兄弟拎啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T07:22:31.000Z","msg":"沙特, UAE : 不了, 我地大佬係美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49fb9c71b59b26b84b160a625667f20dbc52c36","tid":854100,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T07:23:39.000Z","msg":"疤爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ac7b33786209c667f4e52a98a4377f146a4a4e","tid":854100,"uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T07:26:37.000Z","msg":"支爆支爆支爆"},{"pid":"4affd54fcc9b6ddc57722e64adcf302d4658b2da","tid":854100,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ddb9afeb79aaf7c1c362f2bd301a8bd0c49372","tid":854100,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T07:31:34.000Z","msg":"一帶一路白手套 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2446bc591a82d0b72d2e38038ef99d4aa65f3836","tid":854100,"uid":35430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-